data.description: *** seller offering $5000 credit, if closing by12/20!!  SELLER IS MOTIVATED BRING OFFERS The beautiful all brick ranch home has SOO MUCH SPACE. Full finished basement. 2 car attached garage. Open Kitchen/Dining/Family Room Area. Stainless steel Appliances, granite counter tops, and backsplash all recently updated!! Rooms are spacious and then the Master suite..is just that  A GORGEOUS SUITE complete with a walk-in closet and enormous bathroom. Downstairs you will find TONS of additional living space...also a unique extra garage entry on the side of the house that leads to A TON of unfinished storage area downstairs.  Home is absolutely gorgeous inside as well as outside....with a fenced in yard, pool, koi pond and deck. So much to see!!  Schedule a showing today this beautiful HOME won't last!!
